s\nchromosphere structure, as well as to the orbital period change during nova\neruptions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Apr 2021 18:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2021 11:45:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-18"}
