 a higher-order\ntriple-point metal in applied strain. The generalization to spinful systems, in\nparticular to the WC-type triple-point material class, is briefly outlined.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Apr 2021 18:00:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Feb 2022 18:42:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Aug 2022 17:31:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-25"}
