h observed spectral-temporal differences in the\nrepeating and one-off FRBs, e.g. longer duration ( smaller flux density ) of\nrepeating FRBs than duration ( flux density ) of one-off FRBs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Apr 2021 02:55:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 23 Jul 2021 00:48:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
